These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, western, animation, family, zombie, sports, thriller
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, salsa, house, punk, techno, metal, pop
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skiing, handball, badminton, soccer, baseball, rugby, basketball
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the fan of salsa and the fan of funk##2
 4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the fan of punk is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person watching zombie movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of house##1
11. the fan of metal is the person watching family movies##1
12. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
13. the person who's sport is skiing is the fan of techno##1
14. the person watching sports movies is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | epic     | sports | western | family | thriller  | animation  |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | punk        | salsa  | pop     | metal   | house       | techno   |
| Sport         | handball   | basketball | soccer    | badminton  | baseball | rugby | skiing |

