.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, australian, french, brazilian, american, russian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, water-polo, ice-hockey, rowing, weightlifting, biathlon, lacrosse
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, tram, quad-bike, jet-ski, van, helicopter
 1. the italian is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is the russian##1
 6. the indonesian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the indonesian is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person driving the helicopter##2
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the australian is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the brazilian is on the right of the indonesian##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is the italian##1
13. the french is on the left of the indonesian##1
14. the french is on the right of the person driving the van##1
15. the italian is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | american | russian      | french     | indonesian  | brazilian | australian | italian |
| Sport         | water-polo  | golf | biathlon | ice-hockey | lacrosse | rowing   | weightlifting  |
| Transport     | tram   | van     | helicopter        | quad-bike  | jet-ski   | snowmobile       | motorbike      |

