The people have 7 different jobs:  doctor, security-guard, fisherman, designer, coach, paramedic, scientist
The people use 7 different means of transport: ship, airplane, car, quad-bike, boat, tram, subway
 1. the person driving the airplane is the doctor##1
 2. the person driving the boat is the designer##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the coach##1
 4. the person driving the car is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the subway and the scientist##2
 6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the left of the scientist##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
10. the fisherman is on the right of the paramedic##1
11. the person driving the airplane is the doctor##1
12. the fisherman is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the designer##1
14. the person driving the subway is the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
