 3. the thai is the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating broccoli is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the brazilian is the person watching spy movies##1
10. the indonesian is the person eating apple##1
11. the person watching romance movies is the british##1
12. the person eating peas is the russian##1
13. the spanish is on the far right##1
14. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching crime movies##2
15. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
