.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  chef, pilot, journalist, bartender, security-guard, social-worker, designer
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, disco, techno, r&b, funk, classical, folk
7 different pets are kept: cat, frog, goldfish, horse, pony, hamster, goat
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the journalist##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is between the fan of funk and the fan of techno##2
 3. the fan of jazz is the owner of the frog##1
 4. the fan of folk is on the left of the social-worker##1
 5. the fan of jazz is the chef##1
 6. the journalist is in the middle##1
 7. the security-guard is the fan of classical##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the fan of jazz is the owner of the frog##1
10. the designer is the owner of the pony##1
11. the chef is on the right of the bartender##1
12. the fan of folk is on the left of the social-worker##1
13. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
14. the fan of disco is on the left of the chef##1
15. the designer is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | pilot | social-worker | security-guard | journalist  | designer   | bartender | chef      |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno        | classical    | funk     | r&b     | disco   | jazz        |
| Pet           | cat   | goldfish       | hamster    | horse | pony | goat   | frog |

