.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, board-games, reading, sudoku, collecting, fishing, camping
7 different pets are kept: bird, cat, ferret, pony, snake, mouse, rabbit
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, airplane, roller, skateboard, motorbike, tram, subway
 1. the person driving the subway is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 2. the person driving the subway is the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the snake##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the mouse##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is the person driving the train##1
15. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | reading  | fishing | sudoku  | camping | board-games | collecting | writing |
| Pet         | pony | ferret    | bird        | snake      | mouse     | cat   | rabbit |
| Transport   | roller  | airplane   | motorbike | tram        | skateboard    | subway  | train   |

