.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, social-worker, engineer, teacher, coach, doctor, musician
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, family, musical, romance, fantasy, thriller
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, cycling, rugby, baseball, swimming, parkour
 1. the teacher is on the left of the musician##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the doctor is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the musician is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the social-worker##1
12. the person who's sport is sailing is between the engineer and the person who's sport is swimming##2
13. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1
15. the librarian is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
