.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, water, lemonade, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, drawing, video-games, puzzles, reading, woodworking, hiking
7 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, rat, dog, pony, fish, mouse
 1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 4. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the fish is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the owner of the dog is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the owner of the rat##2
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
14. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
15. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | juice  | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   | lemonade        | water     | mirinda | milk       |
| Hobby      | camping | drawing | hiking | puzzles | video-games  | reading   | woodworking |
| Pet        | mouse   | turtle     | goat     | fish      | pony | dog    | rat      |

 